text: Nizhnekargino () is a rural locality (a selo) in Asyanovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 188 as of 2010. There are 3 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Dyurtyuli, 3 km from Asyanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Nizhnekargino
